{
  "stem": "13313.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's only-- I'm adjusting for the-- for the tunnel vision I have because of my age, but otherwise I would thought they would be much older.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I would say in their mid '40s.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, as I said, they had no children, so Mother negotiated with them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said, how would you like to-- also, don't forget that they did business with our-- our place was closed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how, whether they did a lot of business with non-Jewish enterprises, but the business wasn't flourishing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother said, look we have money, and we don't know how long this is going to last.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But how would you-- how-- how would you like to move to a-- to the countryside, rent a little cottage, and take on my children under your name and-- and-- and hide them?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And keep them, and lived there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I'm going to go in hiding myself, and I will keep you supplied for rental money and whatever it costs on ongoing basis, from my hiding place.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They found-- they had relatives.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Their own-- the lady, the-- the-- that I'm talking about, she had her own siblings and parents in a small village south of the city of Antwerp, on the highway to Brussels.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was called, Hove, H-O-V-E.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name was Roggeman, R-O-G-G-E-M-A-N.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jose, which is short for Josephine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was Caesar-- Caesar.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Caesar and Jose Roggeman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Catholic people.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So for a few days while they were organizing the little cottage that they rented, which was in a little side street, very quiet side street, was more of a path than a street, although it had that name, it was called the [?",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
